            <title>[CASSANDRA-17415] dropping of a materialized view does not create a snapshot with dropped- prefix</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17415</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When auto_snapshot: true and MV is dropped, the name of the snapshot does not start with &quot;dropped-&quot; prefix as a normal table would. This is an issue for 3.11.x only. In 4.x, the code was refactored a lot and it does not happen there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
